'''Dat-an''' was the [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Annoo-dat Prime]]. After they left their [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Annoo (original)|Annoo]] and conquered [[Annoo (Gelefil)|Gelefil]], the language was also adopted by the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] other inhabitants, the [[Annoo-dat Blue]], largely replacing [[Tra'ang'a]].

